snippet.title: Worms Revolution Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Worms Revolution Launch Trailer. Join us on Facebook & Twitter http://facebook.com/GameNewsOfficial & http://twitter.com/gamenewstrailer.

Worms Revolution Launch Trailer. The game will be available on PC, PS3 (PSN) and Xbox 360 (XBLA). Subscribe now to get the latest gameplay trailers, walkthrough and ingame videos !
